author: Nerd of the Rings
description:
I'll be chatting live with Thomas from Burgschneider - hosts of the first ever licensed Middle-earth LARP event!  The Brandywine Festival is taking place October 7-12, 2025.  Tickets are exclusively available via the kickstarter for the event: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/burgschneiderlarp/middle-earth-adventures-the-brandywine-festival

I'll be helping out with some of the lore elements, including things like activities, quest lines, and story!  Join us on this stream as we talk about some of the things we are working on, and answer any questions you may have!

#brandywinefestival #larp #tolkien
title: Open Q&A with The Brandywine Festival
